      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CRUISING JAMIE (4) is first up since finishing eighth (26.16) in a Grade 5 H at this track over 450m 12 weeks ago. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Well placed here and will can go close with a clear run. ASTON CLEESE (2) goes very well this course and distance starting 12 times for four wins and two minors. Below best last time at this track (22.72) in a Grade 5, finishing a 5 length fourth. Makes strong appeal on best. WILLOW'S GIRL (3) turned in a plain effort last time when seventh at Geelong over 400m behind Just Believe (23.33) in a Grade 5. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Should be in this for a long way. ASTON GIRL (1) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
